port & Operations\",\n294 |       legal_compliance: \"Legal, Risk & Compliance\",\n295 |       supply_chain: \"Supply Chain & Logistics\",\n296 |       finance_accounting: \"Finance, Audit & Accounting\",\n297 |       it_engineering: \"IT Service & Infrastructure\",\n298 |       hr_admin: \"People & Administrative Services\"\n299 |     }[opFunction] || \"Operations\";\n300 | \n301 |     const reportMd = `# GFF AI // ENTERPRISE SOVEREIGN ROI SIMULATION REPORT\n302 | Generated: ${new Date().toLocaleDateString()}\n303 | Status: MODELLED - ILLUSTRATIVE ONLY\n304 | \n305 | ## I. ORGANIZATIONAL CONTEXT & PROFILE\n306 | - Industry Sector: ${indName}\n307 | - Enterprise Scale: ${sizeName}\n308 | - Operational Function: ${funcName}\n309 | - Implementation Horizon: ${implementationHorizon.replace(\"_\", \" \")}\n310 | \n311 | ## II. FINANCIAL & OPERATIONAL BASELINE (INPUTS)\n312 | - Annual Operational Cost Baseline: $${annualCostBaseline.toLocaleString()}\n313 | - Current Manual Friction Index: ${manualEffort.toUpperCase()}\n314 | - Modelled Addressable Manual Overhead: $${addressableCostBaseline.toLocaleString()}\n315 | - Annual Process Volume: ${processVolume.toLocaleString()} units\n316 | - Average Handling Time: ${avgHandlingTime ? avgHandlingTime + \" Minutes\" : \"Not Specified (estimated based on sector average)\"}\n317 | - Estimated Loaded Hourly Rate: $${loadedHourlyRate}/hr\n318 | - Estimated Current Manual Effort: ${manualHoursSpent.toLocaleString()} hours/year\n319 | \n320 | ## III. TARGET SOVEREIGN PARAMETERS\n321 | - Automation Target Rate: ${automationTarget}%\n322 | - Expected Productivity Boost: ${productivityImprovement}%\n323 | - Enclave Platform Investment CapEx: $${initialInvestment.toLocaleString()}\n324 | - Strategic Priority Lens: ${currentPriorityObj.title} (${priority.toUpperCase()})\n325 | \n326 | ## IV. KEY RECOVERY METRICS (EXPECTED CASE)\n327 | - Illustrative Annual Reclaimed Value: $${expectedGrossSavings.toLocaleString()}\n328 | - Estimated Ann