ad\", icon: \"👥\" },\n 934 |                       { id: \"governance-approach\", label: \"Governance Approach\", icon: \"⚖️\" },\n 935 |                       { id: \"success-measures\", label: \"Success Measures\", icon: \"📈\" },\n 936 |                       { id: \"assumptions\", label: \"Assumptions\", icon: \"📝\" },\n 937 |                       { id: \"risks-mitigations\", label: \"Risks & Mitigations\", icon: \"🔒\" },\n 938 |                       { id: \"next-steps\", label: \"Next Steps\", icon: \"🏁\" }\n 939 |                     ].map((sec, idx) => (\n 940 |                       <button\n 941 |                         key={sec.id}\n 942 |                         onClick={() => {\n 943 |                           setActivePreviewSection(sec.id);\n 944 |                           const el = document.getElementById(sec.id);\n 945 |                           if (el) el.scrollIntoView({ behavior: \"smooth\", block: \"start\" });\n 946 |                         }}\n 947 |                         className={`w-full text-left px-2.5 py-1.5 rounded text-[10px] font-mono transition flex items-center gap-2 ${activePreviewSection === sec.id ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] font-bold border-l border-[#009DFF]\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white\"}`}\n 948 |                       >\n 949 |                         <span>{sec.icon}</span>\n 950 |                         <span>{String(idx + 1).padStart(2, \"0\")}. {sec.label}</span>\n 951 |                       </button>\n 952 |                     ))}\n 953 |                   </nav>\n 954 | \n 955 |                   <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 space-y-2\">\n 956 |                     <button onClick={handleCopyOutline} className=\"w-full py-1.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[#00FF9D] border border-white/10 hover:bg-[#00FF9D]/10 hover:text-[#00FF9D] transition text-[9px] font-mono uppercase font-semibold\">\n 957 |                       {copied ? \"✓ Copied\" : \"Copy Outline\"}\n 958 |           