 audits and continuous zero persistent retention verification.</p>\n1214 |                         </div>\n1215 |                       </div>\n1216 |                     </div>\n1217 |                   </div>\n1218 | \n1219 |                   {/* SECTION 7: GOVERNANCE APPROACH */}\n1220 |                   <div id=\"governance-approach\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1221 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1222 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION VII</span>\n1223 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold font-sans\">⚖️ Governance Approach</h2>\n1224 |                     </div>\n1225 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85 text-left font-sans\">\n1226 |                       <p>\n1227 |                         Sovereign AI deployments mandate strict, zero-trust governance protocols to eliminate data leakage. GFF enforces safety policies directly at the runtime layer:\n1228 |                       </p>\n1229 |                       \n1230 |                       <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030305] print:border-black/10 print:bg-black/5 font-mono text-[9px] space-y-2.5\">\n1231 |                         <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[7px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest\">\n1232 |                           <span>GOVERNANCE PROTOCOL CHECKS</span>\n1233 |                           <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">ENFORCED AT RUNTIME</span>\n1234 |                         </div>\n1235 |                         <ul className=\"space-y-1.5 text-white/60 print:text-black/80 font-light font-mono leading-relaxed\">\n1236 |                           <li className=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n1237 |                             <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">»</span>\n1238 |                             <span><strong>Boundary Isolation:</strong> No prompts or weight matrices leave the single-tenant VPC environment. All model inferences are computed locally.</span>\n1239 |                           </li>\n1240 |                           <li className=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n1241 |                             <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">»</span>\n1242 |                             <span><strong>Memory Scrubbing:</strong> In-memory buffers are hard-flushed instantly after query completion to maintain absolute zero data retention.</span>\n1243 |                           </li>\n1244 |                           <li className=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n1245 |                             <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D]\">»</span>\n1246 |                             <span><strong>Immutable Audit Logs:</strong> Live user transactions generate trace receipts written to a secure read-only compliance ledger.</span>\n1247 |                           </li>\n1248 |                         </ul>\n1249 |                       </div>\n1250 |                     </div>\n1251 |                   </div>\n1252 | \n1253 |                   {/* SECTION 8: SUCCESS MEASURES */}\n1254 |                   <div id=\"success-measures\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1255 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1256 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION VIII</span>\n1257 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold font-sans\">📈 Success Measures</h2>\n1258 |                     </div>\n1259 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-3 print:text-black/85 text-left font-sans\">\n1260 |                       <p>Operational performance metrics and compliance SLAs are tracked in real-time inside the control center:</p>\n1261 |                       \n1262 |                       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-center font-mono\">\n1263 |                         <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10\">\n1264 |                           <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#00FF9D] block print:text-black\">&gt; 99.9%</span>\n1265 |                           <span className=\"text-[7px] text-white/35 uppercase mt-1 block\">Task Efficacy</span>\n1266 |                         </div>\n1267 |                         <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10\">\n1268 |                           <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#009DFF] block print:text-black\">&lt; 150ms</span>\n1269 |                           <span className=\"text-[7px] text-white/35 uppercase mt-1 block\">Decision Latency</span>\n1270 |                         </div>\n1271 |                         <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10\">\n1272 |                           <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#9D00FF] block print:text-black\">0 Trace</span>\n1273 |                           <span className=\"text-[7px] text-white/35 uppercase mt-1 block\">Retention</span>\n1274 |                         </div>\n1275 |                         <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10\">\n1276 |                           <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#E5A93C] block print:text-black\">30%+ Saved</span>\n1277 |                           <span className=\"text-[7px] text-white/35 uppercase mt-1 block\">API OpEx Saved</span>\n1278 |                         </div>\n1279 |                       </div>\n1280 |                     </div>\n1281 |                   </div>\n1282 |                   {/* SECTION 9: ASSUMPTIONS */}\n1283 |                   <div id=\"assumptions\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1284 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1285 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION IX</span>\n1286 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold font-sans\">📝 Assumptions</h2>\n1287 |                     </div>\n1288 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-3 print:text-black/85 text-left font-sans\">\n1289 |                       <p>To guarantee target timeline delivery within the calculated <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.weeks} Weeks</strong> window, we assume:</p>\n1290 |                       <ul className=\"space-y-1 list-disc pl-4 text-white/60 print:text-black/80 font-light\">\n1291 |                         <li>Read-only VPC network interfaces to unindexed legacy database silos are provisioned within 7 business days.</li>\n1292 |                         <li>Key stakeholder sponsors listed (specifically: <strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.stakeholdersLabel}</strong>) participate in weekly alignment syncs.</li>\n1293 |                         <li>Isolated staging clusters are pre-cleared for local sandbox simulation.</li>\n1294 |                       </ul>\n1295 |                     </div>\n1296 |                   </div>\n1297 | \n1298 |                   {/* SECTION 10: RISKS & MITIGATIONS */}\n1299 |                   <div id=\"risks-mitigations\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1300 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1301 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION X</span>\n1302 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold font-sans font-bold\">🔒 Risks & Mitigations</h2>\n1303 |                     </div>\n1304 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n1305 |                       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-left\">\n1306 |                         <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10 space-y-1\">\n1307 |                           <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black font-mono flex items-center gap-1\">⚡ Schema Fragmentation</h4>\n1308 |                           <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70\">Legacy silos inside {pData.org} might contain poorly indexed database schemas, causing query lookup delays.</p>\n1309 |                           <div className=\"pt-1.5 border-t border-white/5 text-[9.5px] text-[#00FF9D] font-mono\">Mitigation: GFF OmniMesh automatically creates a read-only local semantic layer without altering physical tables.</div>\n1310 |                         </div>\n1311 |                         <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.005] print:border-black/10 space-y-1\">\n1312 |                           <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white print:text-black font-mono flex items-center gap-1\">⚡ Provisioning Bottlenecks</h4>\n1313 |                           <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 print:text-black/70\">Lead times for single-tenant cloud instance clearance might delay core systems setup.</p>\n1314 |                           <div className=\"pt-1.5 border-t border-white/5 text-[9.5px] text-[#00FF9D] font-mono\">Mitigation: GFF runs lightweight containerized prototypes on isolated local staging nodes immediately.</div>\n1315 |                         </div>\n1316 |                       </div>\n1317 |                     </div>\n1318 |                   </div>\n1319 | \n1320 |                   {/* SECTION 11: NEXT STEPS */}\n1321 |                   <div id=\"next-steps\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1322 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1323 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50\">SECTION XI</span>\n1324 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold font-sans\">🏁 Next Steps</h2>\n1325 |                     </div>\n1326 |                     <div className=\"text-xs text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed space-y-4 print:text-black/85\">\n1327 |                       <p className=\"text-left font-sans font-light\">To begin the co-innovation deployment of GFF AI within your single-tenant infrastructure, we propose:</p>\n1328 |                       <ol className=\"space-y-2 font-mono text-[9.5px] text-white/60 print:text-black/80 list-decimal pl-4 text-left\">\n1329 |                         <li><strong>Complete SOW Sign-off:</strong> Apply your secure signature stamp using the executive authorization panel below.</li>\n1330 |                         <li><strong>Boundary Discovery Session:</strong> Conduct a 1-hour secure VPC routing and credential clearance call with our Lead Architect.</li>\n1331 |                         <li><strong>Squad Mobilization:</strong> Finalize resource provisioning of suggested squad cohort (<strong className=\"text-white print:text-black font-semibold\">{pData.engagementPathObj.squad}</strong>) in 7 days.</li>\n1332 |                       </ol>\n1333 |                     </div>\n1334 |                   </div>\n1335 |                   {/* EXECUTIVE SOW AUTHORIZATION */}\n1336 |                   <div id=\"sign-off-block\" className=\"scroll-mt-10 space-y-4\">\n1337 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-1 print:border-black/10\">\n1338 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] font-bold uppercase print:text-black/50 font-bold\">AUTHORIZATION</span>\n1339 |                       <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-[#00FF9D] print:text-black flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">✍️ SOW Stamp Sign-Off</h2>\n1340 |                     </div>\n1341 |                     \n1342 |                     <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 space-y-4 print:border-black/10\">\n1343 |                       <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 leading-snug\">\n1344 |                         By entering your signature below, you endorse the draft SOW outline. This is a secure local simulation of the strategic roadmap setup; no contract data is retained.\n1345 |                       </p>\n1346 | \n1347 |                       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n1348 |                         <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n1349 |                           <label htmlFor=\"signatory-name-input\" className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase block cursor-pointer\">Authorized Signatory Name</label>\n1350 |                           <input\n1351 |                             id=\"signatory-name-input\"\n1352 |                             type=\"text\"\n1353 |                             value={signName}\n1354 |                             onChange={(e) => setSignName(e.target.value)}\n1355 |                             placeholder=\"e.g. Dr. Catherine Vance\"\n1356 |                             className=\"w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded px-3 py-2 text-xs text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#00FF9D] print:hidden\"\n1357 |                           />\n1358 |                         </div>\n1359 |                         <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n1360 |                           <label htmlFor=\"corporate-title-input\" className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase block cursor-pointer\">Corporate Title</label>\n1361 |                           <input\n1362 |                             id=\"corporate-title-input\"\n1363 |                             type=\"text\"\n1364 |                             value={signTitle}\n1365 |                             onChange={(e) => setSignTitle(e.target.value)}\n1366 |                             placeholder=\"e.g. VP of Security Compliance\"\n1367 |                             className=\"w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded px-3 py-2 text-xs text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#00FF9D] print:hidden\"\n1368 |                           />\n1369 |                         </div>\n1370 |                       </div>\n1371 | \n1372 |                       <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-2\">\n1373 |                         {!isSigned ? (\n1374 |                           <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n1375 |                             <button\n1376 |                               type=\"button\"\n1377 |                               onClick={() => {\n1378 |                                 if (signName.trim() && signTitle.trim()) {\n1379 |                                   setIsSigned(true);\n1380 |                                   setValidationErrors((prev) => {\n1381 |                                     const next = { ...prev };\n1382 |                                     delete next.signature;\n1383 |                                     return next;\n1384 |                                   });\n1385 |                                 } else {\n1386 |                                   setValidationErrors((prev) => ({\n1387 |                                     ...prev,\n1388 |                                     signature: \"Please enter both Signatory Name and Title before applying your digital a